1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:04,033
for the next steps we are going to need more minerals

2
00:00:04,133 --> 00:00:06,833
single block miners are too much of an hassle

3
00:00:06,833 --> 00:00:09,633
and we can't wait for god to gift us more transceiver

4
00:00:09,633 --> 00:00:11,800
so we will have to ask AE2

5
00:00:13,266 --> 00:00:15,866
we also need some more preparations

6
00:00:16,866 --> 00:00:18,000
and off we go

7
00:00:32,266 --> 00:00:36,033
next, we shall fix some issues with the old assline layout

8
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:38,266
GregTech pipes did the trick

9
00:00:38,866 --> 00:00:44,266
we will also need an assembly line capable of handling more complex recipes

10
00:00:44,533 --> 00:00:47,800
we can do that using Steve's Factory Manager mod

11
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:51,200
for example in the normal assline

12
00:00:51,233 --> 00:00:56,033
we can't have recipes that have the same item spread across multiples buses

13
00:00:56,033 --> 00:00:58,200
like the heavy duty plates

14
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:02,500
moving on, we also have to worry about Lutetium

15
00:01:02,833 --> 00:01:04,733
we are not making enough of it

16
00:01:05,033 --> 00:01:07,333
the main issue is cooling down the water

17
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:10,400
so let's craft some more turbines

18
00:01:11,233 --> 00:01:14,533
and we don't have to forget to order a new rocket

19
00:01:15,666 --> 00:01:17,466
while AE2 is busy

20
00:01:17,466 --> 00:01:21,266
I think it's a good time for us to touch some grass

21
00:01:21,533 --> 00:01:23,000
in LuV style

22
00:01:23,166 --> 00:01:27,133
so let's make some genetically modified plants

23
00:01:36,133 --> 00:01:38,800
and here we go, a nice plant

24
00:01:39,233 --> 00:01:44,733
in the meanwhile, we also have increased the UU matter and the Lutetium production

25
00:01:45,833 --> 00:01:50,066
we have 32 fluid reactor fueling a GT++ boiler

26
00:01:50,066 --> 00:01:52,466
feeding four XL turbines

27
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:56,733
and I have lost count of the amount of miners we have

28
00:01:58,133 --> 00:02:01,600
next, we are going to do a little bit more of the mozline

29
00:02:01,666 --> 00:02:03,800
so that we can have some cerium

30
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,466
we need it for the weird alloy

31
00:02:06,466 --> 00:02:08,200
needed for the precision assembler

32
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,966
needed for the neutron activator

33
00:02:09,966 --> 00:02:11,266
needed for the naqudah line

34
00:02:11,266 --> 00:02:13,800
needed for stuff that we will find out

35
00:02:14,533 --> 00:02:16,666
we also need some lithium Chloride

36
00:02:16,666 --> 00:02:19,533
which apparently can only be made by this recipe

37
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:23,666
so time for some manual LuV work

38
00:02:24,166 --> 00:02:28,000
first we locate some mineral using the LuV tools

39
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,666
next we gather the material

40
00:02:31,466 --> 00:02:32,633
we process it

41
00:02:34,666 --> 00:02:37,200
and finally we void it

42
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:42,233
that way we can feel the frustration needed to take a break from that game

43
00:02:42,266 --> 00:02:43,333
but don't worry

44
00:02:43,333 --> 00:02:46,166
we will probably get back to it in a few hours

45
00:02:52,366 --> 00:02:53,366
welcome back

46
00:02:53,366 --> 00:02:56,333
as you can see we are low on energy

47
00:02:56,333 --> 00:03:00,200
so let's use this time to see what happened during the break

48
00:03:00,633 --> 00:03:03,566
we have managed to make two precision assemblers

49
00:03:03,566 --> 00:03:04,833
and a fusion reactor

50
00:03:05,533 --> 00:03:08,800
we have also made some improvements here and there

51
00:03:09,066 --> 00:03:12,800
now we just complete the monozite and naquadah line

52
00:03:13,266 --> 00:03:19,466
okay now I think we should make a couple more of fusion reactors mk1 before moving on

53
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:23,266
one will be dedicated for an early fusion energy production

54
00:03:23,266 --> 00:03:26,533
and one to double the processing speed of AE2

55
00:03:27,333 --> 00:03:28,766
and here we go

56
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:34,633
this is just a small plant just for sustaining us while we will be working at the bigger versions

57
00:03:34,933 --> 00:03:38,666
as you can see we have now doubled our power production

58
00:03:38,833 --> 00:03:39,966
you might be wondering

59
00:03:39,966 --> 00:03:42,666
what we are going to use all of that power for

60
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:45,133
but I think the answer is obvious

61
00:03:45,733 --> 00:03:47,233
cobblestone

62
00:03:49,233 --> 00:03:50,800
a lot of cobblestone

63
00:03:52,466 --> 00:03:55,833
and I think we should do some cable management now

64
00:03:56,933 --> 00:03:57,866
like that

65
00:03:57,966 --> 00:04:01,733
I wish we could have used lasers since they sound cool

66
00:04:01,733 --> 00:04:03,833
but we cannot craft them yet

67
00:04:04,466 --> 00:04:06,066
we have now a better farm

68
00:04:06,066 --> 00:04:08,300
and the old one is only 18 TPS

69
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:10,866
I think it's time to get rid of it

70
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:14,500
you served us really well, old friend

71
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,933
but it's time to say goodbye

72
00:04:16,966 --> 00:04:20,233
let's do it a bit in vanilla 5 years old style

73
00:04:20,233 --> 00:04:22,666
and a bit in tech it classic style

74
00:04:36,866 --> 00:04:40,533
next we upgrade the ebfs a little bit more

75
00:04:41,166 --> 00:04:43,466
so that we can run out of power

76
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,666
again

77
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:48,933
if we do not want to give up our cobblestone production

78
00:04:48,933 --> 00:04:51,666
we must increase our power production

79
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:56,266
right now the best way is to step up our fusion game

80
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:59,566
let's craft a couple of MK2 reactors

81
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:03,166
by the way this is netherstar setup

82
00:05:03,533 --> 00:05:07,266
and here we farm shrooms to keep ourselves high

83
00:05:08,033 --> 00:05:08,833
I mean

84
00:05:08,833 --> 00:05:10,000
high on vis

85
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,066
anyways this is for crafting

86
00:05:13,733 --> 00:05:15,533
and this for power production

87
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:20,200
do you guys know what access to fusion tier 2 means

88
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,800
correct, many things

89
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:25,466
and the one you thought is probably in the list

90
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:30,533
let's start by using one of our many assembly lines to craft a armor

91
00:05:30,566 --> 00:05:32,133
since there are a few bugs

92
00:05:32,133 --> 00:05:35,233
and we won't be using many times this recipe

93
00:05:35,233 --> 00:05:38,033
this time we can craft it by hand

94
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:43,733
we have to manually place each ingredient inside each bus in the correct order

95
00:05:43,733 --> 00:05:44,566
let's do it

96
00:05:46,033 --> 00:05:49,200
and after fixing some charge issues

97
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,200
we finally can fly fast

98
00:05:52,866 --> 00:05:57,366
by the way we now even have one of these cool advanced assembly lines

99
00:05:57,366 --> 00:05:59,400
which can even turn orange

100
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:02,233
they now do look like proper traffic lights

101
00:06:03,666 --> 00:06:06,466
and after cooking some neutronium

102
00:06:06,466 --> 00:06:08,933
we finally unlocked the UV age

103
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,333
now we rush a UV assembler

104
00:06:12,333 --> 00:06:17,166
and finally, we have access to a proper way of transporting energy

105
00:06:17,233 --> 00:06:19,166
nothing can stop us now

106
00:06:19,966 --> 00:06:21,866
just look at how cool they look

107
00:06:21,866 --> 00:06:24,366
and think about how much power they carry

108
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,000
now as they say

109
00:06:27,033 --> 00:06:30,200
from great power comes great responsibility

110
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:34,800
so let's gather some materials for the next upgrade of our fusion plant

111
00:06:46,833 --> 00:06:49,266
and this is the best we can do right now

112
00:06:49,566 --> 00:06:52,033

we should probably look into tin plasma though


113
00:06:52,933 --> 00:06:56,400
anyways as you can see from the screen behind me

114
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:59,966
this is barely enough to make our energy meter measure something

115
00:07:00,233 --> 00:07:01,833
this is not good at all

116
00:07:02,133 --> 00:07:03,566
we need more power

117
00:07:04,366 --> 00:07:06,600
the best route right now is probably

118
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:10,333
to step further up our fusion tier to unlock better recipes

119
00:07:10,533 --> 00:07:15,666
however, we miserable carbon based life forms can't manage that

120
00:07:15,933 --> 00:07:19,266
we need the help of silicon based life forms

121
00:07:19,466 --> 00:07:22,733
and the only one who can help us create life is

122
00:07:23,433 --> 00:07:23,833
god

123
00:07:24,466 --> 00:07:26,633
we first have to take some bacteria

124
00:07:26,633 --> 00:07:28,966
and seal it inside a petri dish

125
00:07:29,633 --> 00:07:34,600
next we start multiplying this culture into a bacterial vat

126
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,400
we must be careful

127
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:39,066
and not let this stuff escape the vat

128
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:40,933
and we shall not eat it

129
00:07:41,166 --> 00:07:43,400
I know that this stuff looks appealing

130
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,033
but just don't eat it

131
00:07:45,266 --> 00:07:49,733
we have to let the population of vat be always at half of the vat space

132
00:07:49,733 --> 00:07:51,800
to maximize its reproduction

133
00:07:52,466 --> 00:07:56,466
and finally, we can use this stuff to make some growth medium

134
00:07:56,466 --> 00:07:58,366
for our stem cells

135
00:07:59,233 --> 00:08:03,000
now we just have to do questionable things to these poor cells

136
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,233
until we get a wetware processor

137
00:08:05,366 --> 00:08:08,266
however a single processor won't be enough

138
00:08:08,266 --> 00:08:11,666
we have to merge many of them to form a single mainframe

139
00:08:11,666 --> 00:08:14,933
however to connect wires and neurons

140
00:08:14,933 --> 00:08:17,533
we need first to do some more research

141
00:08:17,533 --> 00:08:20,233
and apparently, our scanners won't cut it

142
00:08:20,233 --> 00:08:23,166
we have to build a full fledged research station

143
00:08:23,166 --> 00:08:27,033
capable of using the computation power from a quantum computer

144
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,033
and this is the complete setup

145
00:08:29,366 --> 00:08:31,700
we have made a 12 racks computer

146
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:34,433
for a total of 420 computation

147
00:08:34,433 --> 00:08:36,666
to keep the research time short

148
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:39,200
we make certain the cat is okay

149
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,433
so that the computer is certain

150
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:47,600
we place a data stick and the object we want to study in the research station

151
00:08:50,566 --> 00:08:52,666
next we turn on the computer

152
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,766
we have to be careful at how much power it drains

153
00:08:55,766 --> 00:08:57,333
and how much it heats up

154
00:09:01,366 --> 00:09:03,666
and finally we start researching

155
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:12,200
and here we have our results

156
00:09:12,366 --> 00:09:15,566
we must always remember to turn off the PC

157
00:09:15,566 --> 00:09:17,566
or we will have a high Bill to pay

158
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:20,233
now we move to the production facility

159
00:09:20,233 --> 00:09:22,733
and put the data in the assembly line

160
00:09:24,533 --> 00:09:27,933
and finally we ask AE2 to start it

161
00:09:28,733 --> 00:09:31,366
next we shall go to new weird planets

162
00:09:31,366 --> 00:09:34,466
visit their oceans and collect some weeds

163
00:09:36,566 --> 00:09:42,200
and do some biological experiments on them to extrapolate extraterrestrial bacteria

164
00:09:42,466 --> 00:09:45,400
next we shall realize that in all of that time

165
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:50,066
our mega blast furnace has polluted our world a little bit too much

166
00:09:50,766 --> 00:09:52,866
we fought some weird bosses

167
00:09:53,766 --> 00:09:56,000
we increased our power production

168
00:09:57,233 --> 00:10:00,133
we automated some extreme craftings

169
00:10:01,966 --> 00:10:04,266
and crafted an extreme rocket

170
00:10:15,633 --> 00:10:19,533
we fixed the pollution issues by upgrading our mufflers

171
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:24,200
and upgraded the rating of our blast furnace

172
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,666
we made a few more fusion reactors

173
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:32,166
and started using our TNT stockpile

174
00:10:34,866 --> 00:10:37,366
we maxed out our power sub-station

175
00:11:24,466 --> 00:11:27,166
and completed our extreme rocket

176
00:11:55,033 --> 00:11:57,266
we built a PCB factory

177
00:11:59,766 --> 00:12:04,000
and we looked up on how to have the materials to make PCBs

178
00:13:06,566 --> 00:13:09,333
and we are getting the last tier of bio-circuit

179
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:04,033

下面我们需要更多的矿物


180
00:00:04,133 --> 00:00:06,833
单方块矿机太麻烦了

181
00:00:06,833 --> 00:00:09,633
我们等不及上帝给我们更多的超立方体了

182
00:00:09,633 --> 00:00:11,800
所以我们向AE2要一点

183
00:00:13,266 --> 00:00:15,866
我们还需要一些准备

184
00:00:16,866 --> 00:00:18,000
然后，出发

185
00:00:32,266 --> 00:00:36,033
接下来，我们将修复旧装配线布局的一些问题

186
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:38,266
通过使用GT管道

187
00:00:38,866 --> 00:00:44,266
我们还需要一条能够处理更复杂配方的装配线

188
00:00:44,533 --> 00:00:47,800
我们可以使用SFM来做到这一点

189
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:51,200
例如，在正常的装配线中

190
00:00:51,233 --> 00:00:56,033
我们不能使用"在不同仓室之间有相同物品"的配方

191
00:00:56,033 --> 00:00:58,200
比如重型装甲板

192
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:02,500
接下来我们还得担心镥

193
00:01:02,833 --> 00:01:04,733
我们做得还不够

194
00:01:05,033 --> 00:01:07,333
主要问题是冷却水

195
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:10,400
让我们制造更多的涡轮机

196
00:01:11,233 --> 00:01:14,533
我们不用忘记下单新火箭

197
00:01:15,666 --> 00:01:17,466
在AE2忙的时候

198
00:01:17,466 --> 00:01:21,266
我想现在是我们种菜的好时机

199
00:01:21,533 --> 00:01:23,000
以LuV的风格

200
00:01:23,166 --> 00:01:27,133
所以让我们制造一些转基因植物

201
00:01:36,133 --> 00:01:38,800
欧耶，极品作物

202
00:01:39,233 --> 00:01:44,733
与此同时，我们还增加了UU物质和镥的产量

203
00:01:45,833 --> 00:01:50,066
我们有32个流体反应堆给一台GT++热交换机烧开水

204
00:01:50,066 --> 00:01:52,466
热交换机给四个XL涡轮机产生蒸汽

205
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:56,733
我已经数不清有多少矿机了

206
00:01:58,133 --> 00:02:01,600
接下来，我们要再做点独居石产线

207
00:02:01,666 --> 00:02:03,800
这样我们就可以得到一些铈

208
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,466
我们需要它来制造奇怪的合金

209
00:02:06,466 --> 00:02:08,200
来做精密组装机

210
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,966
来做中子活化仪

211
00:02:09,966 --> 00:02:11,266
来做硅岩产线

212
00:02:11,266 --> 00:02:13,800

来做我们之后会需要的东西


213
00:02:14,533 --> 00:02:16,666
我们还需要一些氯化锂

214
00:02:16,666 --> 00:02:19,533
这显然只能由这个配方来做

215
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:23,666

所以是时候进行一些LuV手搓工作了


216
00:02:24,166 --> 00:02:28,000
首先我们用LuV工具找到一些矿物

217
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,666
接下来我们收集材料

218
00:02:31,466 --> 00:02:32,633
处理它

219
00:02:34,666 --> 00:02:37,200
最后销毁它

220
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:42,233
这样我们就能感受到"让我们暂停游戏去休息"所需的挫败感

221
00:02:42,266 --> 00:02:43,333
不过别担心

222
00:02:43,333 --> 00:02:46,166
我们可能会在几个小时重拾信心

223
00:02:52,366 --> 00:02:53,366
欢迎回来

224
00:02:53,366 --> 00:02:56,333
如你所见，我们电力不足

225
00:02:56,333 --> 00:03:00,200
所以让我们利用这段时间看看休息时发生了什么

226
00:03:00,633 --> 00:03:03,566
我们成功地制造了两台精密组装机

227
00:03:03,566 --> 00:03:04,833
和核聚变反应堆

228
00:03:05,533 --> 00:03:08,800
我们也四处做了一些改进

229
00:03:09,066 --> 00:03:12,800
现在我们刚刚完成了独居石线和硅岩线

230
00:03:13,266 --> 00:03:19,466
好吧，我想我们应该在继续之前再做几个聚变堆mk1

231
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:23,266
一个将用于早期聚变能源生产

232
00:03:23,266 --> 00:03:26,533
一个给AE2处理速度翻倍

233
00:03:27,333 --> 00:03:28,766
做好了

234
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:34,633
这只是一个小的工厂，为了在我们制作
更大的聚变堆时，给我们维持电力的

235
00:03:34,933 --> 00:03:38,666
正如你见，我们现在已经将发电量翻了一番

236
00:03:38,833 --> 00:03:39,966
你可能想知道

237
00:03:39,966 --> 00:03:42,666
我们要用这些能量做什么？

238
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:45,133
但我想答案是显而易见的

239
00:03:45,733 --> 00:03:47,233
圆石

240
00:03:49,233 --> 00:03:50,800
很多圆石

241
00:03:52,466 --> 00:03:55,833
我想我们现在应该整理电线

242
00:03:56,933 --> 00:03:57,866
像这样

243
00:03:57,966 --> 00:04:01,733
我希望能使用激光，因为它们听起来很酷

244
00:04:01,733 --> 00:04:03,833
但我们还不能制造它们

245
00:04:04,466 --> 00:04:06,066
我们现在有一个更好的农场

246
00:04:06,066 --> 00:04:08,300
而旧的只有18 TPS

247
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:10,866
我想是时候摆脱它了

248
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:14,500
你已尽职尽责了，老友

249
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,933
但是时候说再见了

250
00:04:16,966 --> 00:04:20,233
让我们用5岁小孩玩MC的风格做一点

251
00:04:20,233 --> 00:04:22,666
用古典科技风做一点

252
00:04:36,866 --> 00:04:40,533
接下来我们升级一下高炉

253
00:04:41,166 --> 00:04:43,466

这样我们就可以又一次


254
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,666

电力短缺


255
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:48,933
如果我们不想放弃我们的圆石生产

256
00:04:48,933 --> 00:04:51,666
我们必须增加发电量

257
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:56,266
现在最好的办法是加强核聚变

258
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:59,566
让我们制作几个MK2反应堆

259
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:03,166
顺便说一句，这是下界之星的产线

260
00:05:03,533 --> 00:05:07,266

在这里我们种植蘑菇让我们飞起来


261
00:05:08,033 --> 00:05:08,833
我的意思是

262
00:05:08,833 --> 00:05:10,000

vis的量飞起来


263
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,066
不管怎样，这是用来做配方的

264
00:05:13,733 --> 00:05:15,533
这是用来发电的

265
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:20,200
你们知道有二级核聚变意味着什么吗

266
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,800
对的，很多事情

267
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:25,466
你在想的那个可能就在其中

268
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:30,533
让我们选众多装配线中的一条开始制作装备

269
00:05:30,566 --> 00:05:32,133
因为有一些bug

270
00:05:32,133 --> 00:05:35,233
我们不会多次使用这个配方

271
00:05:35,233 --> 00:05:38,033

这次我们可以手动制作


272
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:43,733
我们必须手动将每个材料
按正确的顺序放入每个仓室中

273
00:05:43,733 --> 00:05:44,566
让我们开始吧

274
00:05:46,033 --> 00:05:49,200
在解决了无线充电问题后

275
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,200
我们终于可以飞得很快了

276
00:05:52,866 --> 00:05:57,366
顺便说一句，我们现在甚至有一条很酷的进阶装配线

277
00:05:57,366 --> 00:05:59,400
它甚至可以变成橙色

278
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:02,233
它们现在看起来确实像真正的交通灯

279
00:06:03,666 --> 00:06:06,466

在烧了一些中子之后


280
00:06:06,466 --> 00:06:08,933
我们终于解锁了UV电压

281
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,333
现在我们速通一个UV组装机

282
00:06:12,333 --> 00:06:17,166
最后，我们有了合适的运输能源的方法

283
00:06:17,233 --> 00:06:19,166
现在没有什么能阻止我们

284
00:06:19,966 --> 00:06:21,866
看看他们看起来有多酷

285
00:06:21,866 --> 00:06:24,366
想想它们携带了多少能量

286
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,000
现在正如他们所说

287
00:06:27,033 --> 00:06:30,200
能力越大，责任越大

288
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:34,800
所以让我们为核聚变工厂的下一次升级收集一些材料

289
00:06:46,833 --> 00:06:49,266
这是我们现在能做的最好的了

290
00:06:49,566 --> 00:06:52,033

我们也许应该研究一下锡等离子


291
00:06:52,933 --> 00:06:56,400
不管怎样，正如你从我身后的屏幕上看到的那样

292
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:59,966
这根本填不满我们的主电网

293
00:07:00,233 --> 00:07:01,833
这一点都不好

294
00:07:02,133 --> 00:07:03,566
我们需要更多能量

295
00:07:04,366 --> 00:07:06,600
现在最好的路线可能是

296
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:10,333
进一步提升聚变等级来解锁更好的配方

297
00:07:10,533 --> 00:07:15,666
然而，我们可怜的碳基生命形式无法做到这一点

298
00:07:15,933 --> 00:07:19,266
我们需要硅基生命形式的帮助

299
00:07:19,466 --> 00:07:22,733
唯一能帮助我们创造生命的人是

300
00:07:23,433 --> 00:07:23,833
上帝

301
00:07:24,466 --> 00:07:26,633
我们首先得取些细菌

302
00:07:26,633 --> 00:07:28,966
并将其密封在培养皿中

303
00:07:29,633 --> 00:07:34,600
接下来，我们在细菌培养缸中繁殖菌群

304
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,400
我们必须小心

305
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:39,066
别让这些东西从培养缸里跑出来

306
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:40,933
我们最好不要吃它

307
00:07:41,166 --> 00:07:43,400
我知道这东西看起来很吸引人

308
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,033
但千万别吃

309
00:07:45,266 --> 00:07:49,733
我们必须让培养缸的输出仓半满

310
00:07:49,733 --> 00:07:51,800
以最大化细菌繁殖

311
00:07:52,466 --> 00:07:56,466
最后，我们可以用它来制造生长培养基

312
00:07:56,466 --> 00:07:58,366
来做干细胞

313
00:07:59,233 --> 00:08:03,000
现在我们只需要对这些可怜的细胞做一些可疑的事情

314
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,233
直到我们得到湿件处理器

315
00:08:05,366 --> 00:08:08,266
然而，单个处理器是不够的

316
00:08:08,266 --> 00:08:11,666
我们得把它们合并成一个单一的主机

317
00:08:11,666 --> 00:08:14,933
然而，要连接电线和神经元

318
00:08:14,933 --> 00:08:17,533
我们首先需要做更多的研究

319
00:08:17,533 --> 00:08:20,233
很明显我们的扫描仪做不到

320
00:08:20,233 --> 00:08:23,166
我们必须建立一个成熟的研究站

321
00:08:23,166 --> 00:08:27,033
能够使用量子计算机的计算能力

322
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,033
这是完成之后的样子

323
00:08:29,366 --> 00:08:31,700
我们做了一台12机架的计算机

324
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:34,433
总共420算力

325
00:08:34,433 --> 00:08:36,666
以缩短研究耗时

326
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:39,200
我们确定薛定谔的猫没事

327
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,433
也就是完成未定元解析

328
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:47,600
我们把闪存和要研究的物品放在研究站里

329
00:08:50,566 --> 00:08:52,666
接下来我们打开计算机

330
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,766
我们必须小心它消耗了多少能量

331
00:08:55,766 --> 00:08:57,333
以及它的热量

332
00:09:01,366 --> 00:09:03,666
最后我们开始研究

333
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:12,200
这是我们的结果

334
00:09:12,366 --> 00:09:15,566
我们必须永远记得关掉计算机

335
00:09:15,566 --> 00:09:17,566

否则我们的电费账单就要爆炸


336
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:20,233
现在我们转移到生产设施

337
00:09:20,233 --> 00:09:22,733
并将数据放入装配线

338
00:09:24,533 --> 00:09:27,933
最后我们要求AE2启动它

339
00:09:28,733 --> 00:09:31,366
接下来我们将去新的奇怪星球

340
00:09:31,366 --> 00:09:34,466
参观他们的海洋，收集一些杂草

341
00:09:36,566 --> 00:09:42,200
并对它们做一些生物学实验来提取外星细菌

342
00:09:42,466 --> 00:09:45,400
接下来，我们将意识到在这段时间里

343
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:50,066
我们的巨高炉对我们的世界造成了太多的污染

344
00:09:50,766 --> 00:09:52,866
我们和一些奇怪的boss战斗

345
00:09:53,766 --> 00:09:56,000
我们增加了发电量

346
00:09:57,233 --> 00:10:00,133
我们自动化了一些梦魇合成

347
00:10:01,966 --> 00:10:04,266
并制作了一个t8火箭

348
00:10:15,633 --> 00:10:19,533
我们通过升级消声仓解决了污染问题

349
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:24,200
并提升了我们高炉的等级

350
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,666
我们又造了几个聚变堆

351
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:32,166

并开始消耗TNT库存


352
00:10:34,866 --> 00:10:37,366
我们把能源站升满级

353
00:11:24,466 --> 00:11:27,166
完成了我们的t8火箭

354
00:11:55,033 --> 00:11:57,266
我们建了一个PCB工厂

355
00:11:59,766 --> 00:12:04,000
我们研究了如何获得制造电路板基板的材料

356
00:13:06,566 --> 00:13:09,333
我们就要拿到最后一级生物电路板了

357
00:01:17,466 --> 00:01:21,266
（touch some grass 还有叫人不要沉迷虚拟世界，要去享受现充生活的意思，但这里采用直译）

